channel.title: Not enough coins?
channel.description:
EDIT: I figured it out. I wasn't putting anything in my shopbuyconfig file haha. Now it's up and working.
I learned how to make shops on my 508 server, so I decided to test it. I put a blue partyhat in there for 1 coin..1 COIN! That's my problem! I have pile of max cash in my inventory and it says "You don't have enough coins to buy this item!" How could I fix this?
